data.description: Potential VA Assumable loan at 2.75%! Check out this charming single-story, 3 bedroom, 1.75 bath residence located in East Hoquiam. Upon entry to the home you are greeted by a spacious living room, bedroom 1 on your right, bedrooms 2&3 and the main bathroom on your left. Through the living room is your full service kitchen and laundry room followed by an oversized great room w/ pellet stove, skylights, pedestal vanity, 3/4 bath and side/back exits. Additionally, the exterior includes a fully fenced back yard, covered back deck, French drain system, utility shed, and detached 2-car garage.
